---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const today = new Date();
const iso = `${today.getFullYear()}-${String(today.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, "0")}-${String(today.getDate()).padStart(2, "0")}`;
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-base-200">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8">
        Effective Date: {iso} • Last Updated: {iso}
      </p>

      <p class="mb-8">
        Light Lane ("we," "our," "us") operates the website <a
          href="https://lightlane.app"
          class="link link-primary"
          rel="noopener"
          target="_blank">https://lightlane.app</a
        > (the "Site") and associated services (the "Services"). This Cookie Policy
        explains how and why cookies and similar tracking technologies are used when
        you visit or interact with our Site and Services.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8">
        By continuing to use our Site or Services, you agree to the use of
        cookies and similar technologies in accordance with this policy. If you
        do not agree, adjust your browser settings or discontinue use of our
        Services.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are small text files placed on your device (computer,
            tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They store information
            about your session and preferences to help improve your browsing
            experience and functionality.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 ml-4 space-y-1">
            <li>
              <strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Automatically deleted when you close
              your browser.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> Remain on your device until deleted
              or expired.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We use cookies and similar technologies for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside ml-4 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Essential Cookies</strong> – Required for the operation of
              our Site and Services (e.g., authentication, session management, security).
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Performance &amp; Analytics Cookies</strong> – Help us understand
              how users interact with our Site to improve navigation, features, and
              performance.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Functional Cookies</strong> – Store user preferences and settings
              to enhance your experience.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Security &amp; Fraud Prevention</strong> – Detect and prevent
              unauthorized access, fraud, and abuse.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Marketing &amp; Retargeting Cookies</strong> – Deliver relevant
              content and ads, and measure effectiveness of campaigns (only if/when
              marketing tracking is introduced).
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We may allow trusted third parties to place cookies on your device
            through our Site to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>
              Provide analytics (e.g., privacy-aware analytics platforms or
              Google Analytics if enabled)
            </li>
            <li>
              Deliver targeted advertising (only if explicitly activated in the
              future)
            </li>
            <li>
              Improve user experience through integrated third-party services
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            These third parties have their own privacy and cookie policies. We
            encourage you to review them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            You can manage cookies through your browser settings, which may
            allow you to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Block all cookies</li>
            <li>Block cookies from specific sites</li>
            <li>Delete existing cookies</li>
            <li>Receive notifications before a cookie is placed</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Disabling certain cookies may impact the functionality and
            performance of our Site and Services.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            5. Legal Basis for Processing Cookies
          </h2>
          <p>We process cookies based on:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Legitimate Interests</strong> – For the operation and security
              of the Services.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Consent</strong> – For non-essential cookies, in compliance
              with applicable privacy laws.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. International Users</h2>
          <p>
            Light Lane operates globally. By using our Site, you acknowledge and
            consent to the transfer and processing of your information in
            jurisdictions where privacy laws may differ from your own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            7. Changes to This Cookie Policy
          </h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update or amend this Cookie Policy at any
            time without prior notice. Updates become effective upon posting to
            the Site.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact:</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:support@lightlane.app" class="link"
              >support@lightlane.app</a
            ><br /><strong>Address:</strong> (Insert Company Address)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
